The Silver Fireballar MKII

Replaces hellfire
this is the MKII of the original Flamethrower
but of course, MKII doesn't mean stronger, its simular, but the MKII works in a diffirent way

Slow firerate
High ignite chance
High elemental damage
High base damage
High blast radius
Slow ammo regen
Silver skin instead of gold
High velocity
High damage
No recoil
Pinpoint accuracy

